<br>
You CAN stack the same exact DoT multiple times on the same mobs from different casters (IE 5 Splurts)<br>
<br>
You CANNOT stack a higher and a lower lvl DoT from diff casters (IE Ignite Blood and another, low lvl DoT from that same line)<br>
<br>
Any combo that stacks solo will stack with multiple necros, so the ignite/splurt/(insert one more DoT that I forget the name here) will all stack.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps!<br>
<br>
